5257ceec5ac01ce9aedd891741a7df3f  owncloud.config.php"
sha256sums="dbd48a2ab9aa19260bbaa0b66fa693488fbcc4d2c01a465cce317545fc813f2c  owncloud-4.5.12.tar.bz2
